44:40.220 --> 44:42.639
I want to insta-print
a couple of sets of business cards.

44:42.806 --> 44:46.393
And I may need your assistance
with printing some posters.

44:47.436 --> 44:49.355
Snow. Snow.

44:49.521 --> 44:51.357
Snow.

46:01.385 --> 46:03.178
I think that's enough.

46:04.471 --> 46:06.265
