46:07.307 --> 46:08.892
Snow.

46:10.519 --> 46:12.646
Don't want to immobilise
the city.

46:33.584 --> 46:36.170
- I thought of snow.
- And it snowed.

46:36.336 --> 46:37.963
What do you know?

46:48.140 --> 46:49.683
I love this place.

46:49.850 --> 46:52.478
Food's not particularly good,
but the ambiance...

46:53.687 --> 46:55.063
