46:55.230 --> 46:56.982
Come on, eat up.

46:57.149 --> 46:59.359
Can't rob a bank
on an empty stomach.

46:59.526 --> 47:00.903
No, I'm not hungry.

47:01.069 --> 47:03.822
Who says you have
to be hungry to eat?

47:03.989 --> 47:05.824
Wasn't supposed to snow today.

47:06.950 --> 47:08.952
