and oranges, OK?

47:28.430 --> 47:30.557
It's reality and fantasy.

47:30.724 --> 47:33.560
Oh, so that's how
the world works!

47:33.727 --> 47:35.479
It's either real
or it's fantasy.

47:35.646 --> 47:37.481
Yeah, that's how
the world works.

47:37.648 --> 47:39.650
Yeah, says the man
who hasn't seen it.

47:39.816 --> 47:43.070
Shadow, at best, you suffer
from a failure of imagination.

47:43.237 --> 47:44.905
We're gonna have to fix that.

47:45.072 --> 47:46.865
Uh-oh, look what
the goat dragged in.

47:47.032 --> 47:48.408
- Cat.
- Goat.

47:48.575 --> 47:50.285
Big, rank, stinking goat.

47:50.452 --> 47:51.954
Mad Sweeney,
you look like a man

47:52.120 --> 47:53.997
who's fallen on hard times
from a great height.

47:54.164 --> 47:55.958
Thought I wasn't gonna see you
until Wisconsin.

47:56.124 --> 47:57.668
